[I'm already downstairs, under your apartment.]

77
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:26,720
[Champ is with me too.]

78
00:10:27,090 --> 00:10:28,580
You can come and you can also go back.

79
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:31,220
Don't come. That's it.

80
00:10:31,220 --> 00:10:32,050
I'm going to sleep.

81
00:10:32,050 --> 00:10:33,880
[I'm not leaving.]

82
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:35,290
[Come down to pick us up right away.]

83
00:10:35,830 --> 00:10:37,900
[Champ brought a lot of food.]

84
