180
00:15:07,010 --> 00:15:08,440
And it's not closed yet.

181
00:15:08,730 --> 00:15:10,880
What does it have to do with you, No?

182
00:15:12,650 --> 00:15:13,480
It has nothing to do with me.

183
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:15,390
I just want to make the excuse sound more sufficient.

184
00:15:18,030 --> 00:15:21,710
Champ, No is cursing your restaurant to go bankrupt.

185
00:15:23,140 --> 00:15:25,420
