188
00:15:30,070 --> 00:15:32,110
Sorry, I didn't mean it.

189
00:15:32,530 --> 00:15:33,430
What in my heart sounds too loud.

190
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:34,860
Come on!

191
00:15:37,220 --> 00:15:38,710
Phugun, don't care about them.

192
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:40,360
Let them talk nonsense.

193
00:15:40,890 --> 00:15:42,310
But I think it's quite fun.

194
00:15:42,310 --> 00:15:44,760
You look close.

195
00:15:46,050 --> 00:15:48,130
I'm his best friend.

196
00:15:48,130 --> 00:15:52,150
I've witnessed every moment of Type's life.

197
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:54,990
If you keep talking, I'll eat it.

198
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:58,240
My chicken, Champ.

199
00:15:58,240 --> 00:16:00,560
-Can you learn to share some with friends?
-There's still so much left.

200
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:03,390
I bought it. And my salary is not as high as yours.

201
00:16:03,390 --> 00:16:06,380
-You talk too much. Eat it.
-What?

202
00:16:07,930 --> 00:16:09,300
Stop fighting!

203
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:12,750
Phu.

204
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:16,560
We've known each other since freshman year.

205
00:16:16,810 --> 00:16:22,190
But Type and No have known each other since middle school. Right?

206
00:16:22,190 --> 00:16:23,050
Yes

207
00:16:23,050 --> 00:16:26,080
How did Brother Champ know you?

208
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:28,480
I lived in the dorm at school since the beginning.

209
00:16:28,850 --> 00:16:30,940
But one day, Type wanted to change rooms.

210
00:16:31,090 --> 00:16:32,490
No came to ask me.

211
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:34,280
But luckily we didn't change.

212
00:16:34,280 --> 00:16:35,170
That's great.

213
00:16:35,660 --> 00:16:38,370
You've been friends for years.

214
00:16:38,370 --> 00:16:40,470
And you look close.

215
00:16:40,710 --> 00:16:41,420
Yes.

216
00:16:41,930 --> 00:16:46,360
You've been dating for seven years, right?

217
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:48,980
Yes, seven years.

218
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:54,030
But I still love Type as I did in the first year.

219
00:16:55,350 --> 00:16:57,110
Here comes the first injury.

220
00:16:58,980 --> 00:17:01,930
Brothers, have you heard of the seven-year itch?

221
00:17:03,050 --> 00:17:04,010
Are you scared?

222
00:17:06,140 --> 00:17:06,890
No.

223
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:09,550
What's there to be afraid of?

224
00:17:11,650 --> 00:17:12,500
Aren't you scared?

225
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:13,470
