229
00:17:24,569 --> 00:17:25,160
What's wrong?

230
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:26,119
I want to vomit.

231
00:17:26,660 --> 00:17:28,270
But I feel sorry for the chicken I ate.

232
00:17:32,370 --> 00:17:34,750
