233
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:37,440
By the way,

234
00:17:37,990 --> 00:17:39,690
did anything bad happen to you two?

235
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:44,510
For me,

236
00:17:44,900 --> 00:17:46,960
