237
00:17:47,790 --> 00:17:51,130
Wait, what does that have to do with the seven-year itch?

238
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:53,940
I'm not afraid.

239
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:57,040
No matter what happens,

240
00:17:58,200 --> 00:18:02,290
I'll hold Type's hand

241
00:18:06,330 --> 00:18:07,840
and get through everything with him.

242
00:18:12,650 --> 00:18:14,590
Champ, call the doctor.

243
00:18:14,590 --> 00:18:16,180
